data.description: OPEN SUN 2-4pm! Nestled in the heart of Salem and built in 1908, the home combines timeless architecture w/ modern updates. The Living Rm leads to a formal Dining Rm then to a light-filled Parlor. The updated Kitchen boasts a Pantry/Laundry Rm. Upstairs, you’ll find three Bedrms & a full Bathrm. For more space, the 720sf Basement is a blank canvas ready for your ideas. Modern comforts include AC, a newer roof, furnace, & water heater. Storage shed, 3 designated park spots plus street, & fenced backyard. Adjacent to the Dining Room is a light-filled Parlor. The large, updated Kitchen leads to an extra-large, fenced backyard perfect for hosting summer barbecues or serene relaxation. On the second level, there are three generously sized Bedrooms and a full Bathroom. If you need even more space, the 720sf basement is a blank canvas ready for your ideas. Modern comforts include central air and a newer roof, furnace, and water heater. Detached Garage and parking.
